Cawan ini kotor.

826
01:17:04.532 --> 01:17:05.658
Helo.

827
01:17:06.409 --> 01:17:09.787
Siapa nama awak?

828
01:17:10.538 --> 01:17:11.748
Long.

829
01:17:13.666 --> 01:17:16.836
